<inglise> 5. </inglise>
<eesti> 5. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the Committee deems it appropriate to do so, it may, in accordance with the Rules of Procedure referred to in Article 6, meet in restricted formation. </inglise>
<eesti> Komitee v&otilde;ib vajaduse korral koguneda piiratud koosseisus vastavalt artiklis 6 osutatud t&ouml;&ouml;korrale. </eesti>
<inglise> In this case, the Council may be represented by the Presidency. </inglise>
